[The spreading of this disease is sad news for the bovine industry, especially the dairy sector. Having incorrect information refuted is critical to keeping accurate information before the public. We are most sorry for those premises facing depopulation. We continue to wish them luck and hope this disease is controlled/eradicated shortly.

